flowchart TD
  A[User opens conversations UI] --> B[e2e_session_controller checks local identity]
  B --> C{Local keys present?}
  C -->|No| D[Generate identity and register prekeys]
  D --> E[Prompt for backup passphrase]
  E --> F[Upload encrypted key backup]
  C -->|Yes| G[Check server bundle and backup state]
  G --> H[Restore on new device if backup exists]
  H --> I[Re-register restored public keys]
  F --> J[Ready to send encrypted messages]
  I --> J
  J --> K[Client encrypts message]
  K --> L[Server stores ciphertext in Message]
  L --> M{Membership changed?}
  M -->|Yes| N[Bump sender_key_version]
  M -->|No| O[Continue encrypted conversation]
  N --> O
